descript.abstract: This dataset represents the Drainage network within the Regional Municipality of Waterloo. The network depicted includes major, minor & intermittent creeks as well as rivers, lakes & ponds that exist in the Region.
descript.purpose: The Drainage dataset was originally developed to display the drainage network on hardcopy and electronic maps. Currently it is used for cartographic representation on hardcopy & digital maps.
